Our Business


North AmericaAustralia
Overview & Contact DetailsUsed Oil Collection & TreatmentProducts

















Products


SUPERFINE™ Transformer Oil
Our premium quality SUPERFINE™ transformer oil meets or exceeds all relevant international standard for unused transformer oil and has been tested and is accepted for use in new transformers. It is also the first carbon neutral transformer oil.
SUPERFINE™ Base Oil
Through our proprietary process, we also re-refine, market and distribute premium quality naphthenic base oil. This high quality base oil is suitable for use in ink and lubricant manufacture and a wide variety or other specialty applications.
Product and Safety Data Sheets

Material Safety Data Sheet: SUPERFINE Base Oil

Material Safety Data Sheet: SUPERFINE Inhibited Base Oil
Material Safety Data Sheet: SUPERFINE Inhibited Transformer Oil

